  "title": "M&E Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>M &amp; E COORDINATOR / SUPERVISOR</strong></p>\n<p><strong>(Building Construction/Project)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>· Site planning, inspections and coordination with consultants, sub-contractors &amp; clients on M&amp;E requirements and specifications</p>\n<p>· Plan, monitor and ensure work-in-progress at site are on schedule</p>\n<p>· Prepare and compile as built drawings for submission</p>\n<p>· Coordinate for submission and approval, all shop drawings, samples, coordination drawings and supervision</p>\n<p>· Identify discrepancies, assess and recommend M&amp;E sub-contractors claims</p>\n<p>· Any other ad hoc duties as assigned by Superioror Management</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>· Recognized Degree / Diploma in Mechanical or Electrical Engineering or equivalent</p>\n<p>· Well versed in AutoCAD</p>\n<p>· Knowledge of BIM would be an added advantage</p>\n<p>· Minimum 2-3 years relevant experience in Singaporein Commercial / Building / Civil Projects, completed at least one project cycle.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
